WEBVTT

00:08:24.672 --> 00:08:31.899
the first controlled airship on air
in Paris for a million people to see.

00:08:31.899 --> 00:08:33.918
Sorry, my American friends,

00:08:33.918 --> 00:08:35.228
I live in North Carolina,

00:08:35.228 --> 00:08:40.110
but it was two years
before the Wright Brothers flew

00:08:40.110 --> 00:08:42.274
on the coast of North Carolina.

00:08:42.274 --> 00:08:44.849
(Applause)

00:08:45.339 --> 00:08:50.117
Flight control is Brazilian.
(Laughter)

00:08:50.117 --> 00:08:53.117
So we went together with these guys

00:08:53.117 --> 00:08:56.018
and we basically put
this exoskeleton together,

00:08:56.018 --> 00:08:59.990
15 degrees of freedom,
hydraulic machine

00:08:59.990 --> 00:09:02.707
that can be commanded by brain signals